products.title: Avocado Toast
products.description: Trendy just got a lot tastier! We’ve adorned our Plain Bagel with a healthy shmear of fresh avocado, then give it the Einstein Bros touch with our very own Everything Spice Mix of sesame seeds, poppy seeds, onion, garlic, caraway seeds, kosher salt and black pepper.

products.title: Hash Brown Side
products.description: We’ve taken Hash Browns to another level. With 4 kinds of cheese and two of our classic shmears, all other Hash Browns have met their match. Add this awesome side to your next egg sandwich.

products.title: Chorizo & Pepper Jack Egg Sandwich
products.description: If you sometimes need a kick in the morning, grab our Chorizo, Pepper Jack, Egg Sandwich. A spicy Chorizo patty topped with soft Pepper Jack cheese gives a traditional egg sandwich the right mix of flavors and spice.

products.title: Coffee Of The Day
products.description: Why be boring? Go beyond “regular or decaf” and explore the world with our Coffee of the Day. These carefully curated coffees and seasonal favorites are brewed every hour to make sure you get a fresh cup, any time of day.

products.title: Hot Tea
products.description: Ready for a steaming cup of comfort? Whatever you’re craving, we’ve got your “cup of tea!” Our Hot Tea selections range from herbal to black, simple to full-flavored.

products.title: Latte
products.description: There’s a “latte” to love about our Latte! Every Latte starts with full-bodied Rainforest Alliance Certified espresso. Then we add perfectly steamed milk of your choice with just a touch of foam to balance out the flavor and deliver a creamy, comforting taste delight.

products.title: Chai Tea Latte
products.description: A little sweet, a little spicy … our Chai Tea Latte highlights the dynamic flavors of India in every perfectly brewed Cup. Steamed milk is combined with black tea embellished with a dynamic blend of sweet and spice for a full-flavor treat.

products.title: Hot Chocolate
products.description: Go ahead, we won’t tell a soul! Nothing comforts like a Hot Chocolate. As cozy as your favorite slippers, every Hot Chocolate is made to order – pick your favorite chocolate (dark, milk, or white!), then top it off with whipped cream.

products.title: Mocha
products.description: Hot chocolate is all grown up! We make your Mocha any way you love it, combining steamed milk and espresso with your favorite: dark chocolate, milk chocolate, or even white chocolate. Capped off with whipped cream, it’s cozy cocoa with a caffeine kick!

products.title: Caramel High Rise
products.description: Elevate your day with this tall drink of delish! Our Caramel High Rise starts with steamed milk and perfectly pulled espresso, then leaps tall buildings of flavor with smooth, satisfying caramel sauce, plus whipped cream and caramel drizzle.

products.title: Chai Tea Latte
products.description: A little sweet, a little spicy … our Chai Tea Latte highlights the dynamic flavors of India in every perfectly brewed Cup. Steamed milk is combined with black tea embellished with a dynamic blend of sweet and spice for a full-flavor treat.

products.title: Hot Tea

products.title: Iced Tea
products.description: It’s an instant thirst-quenching treat in every ice-cold glass! We brew every Iced Tea fresh throughout the day. Choose from a range of caffeinated and decaf brews and take a sip of something truly fresh and refreshing.

products.title: Avocado Toast
products.description: Trendy just got a lot tastier! We’ve adorned our Plain Bagel with a healthy shmear of fresh avocado, then give it the Einstein Bros touch with our very own Everything Spice Mix of sesame seeds, poppy seeds, onion, garlic, caraway seeds, kosher salt and black pepper.

products.title: Potato Roll
products.description: Looking for a light-as-air start to the perfect sandwich? Our Potato Roll is fluffy, potato-y perfection. Pile it high with toppings and dig in. If you're not quite in the mood for a bagel, we understand - our Potato Roll is the next best thing!

products.title: Cinnamon Raisin Bagel
products.description: Cinnamon Raisin Bagel

products.title: Ancient Grain Bagel
products.description: What’s old is new again! Our Ancient Grain Bagel is a fresh new take on the multigrain bagel. This wholesome treat features some oldies-but-goodies: amaranth, chia seeds, quinoa, sunflower seeds, pumpkin seeds, flax and more for a nutrition-packed start to your meal.

products.title: Asiago Cheese Bagel
products.description: Does your bagel speak Italian? Our Asiago Cheese Bagel does! Don’t let the name fool you. This baby has not one, not two, but three cheeses straight from Italy to make the perfect savory start to your day. Asiago, parmesan, romano … Bellissimo!

products.title: Blueberry Bagel
products.description: Looking for sweet, bright, can’t-be-beat flavor? Our Blueberry Bagel tastes like it came straight from the berry patch to your breakfast table! No artificial flavors here – just lovely berries to brighten up every morning.

products.title: Cheesy Hashbrown Bagel
products.description: It’s breakfast on top of breakfast! What could be better? Our Cheesy Hashbrown Gourmet Bagel tops a crowd-favorite Plain Bagel with hashbrown potatoes melted into place with six (count ‘em!) delicious cheeses: mozzarella, provolone, cheddar, parmesan, romano and asiago.

products.title: Chocolate Chip Bagel
products.description: Get in touch with your inner child with our Chocolate Chip Bagel. To really do it right, toast it up to melted-chocolate perfection, then shmear it to your heart’s content for a bit of (slightly sinful) fun in every bite.

products.title: Cinnamon Sugar Bagel
products.description: Sugar and spice and everything nice, all wrapped up in a shmearable bagel! For breakfast, for lunch, or for any time you need an instant mood-boosting treat, our Cinnamon Sugar Bagel is just sweet enough to satisfy.

products.title: Everything Bagel
products.description: You get the whole shebang with our classic Everything Bagel. Each mouthwatering bite delivers a little something to tickle your taste buds, including sesame seeds, poppy seeds, onion, garlic, salt and our exclusive Everything Spice Mix!

products.title: French Toast Bagel
products.description: Our French Toast Bagel gives a whole new meaning to the phrase “Continental Breakfast!” Cinnamon streusel crunch topping, brown sugar and a hint of vanilla transform an ordinary breakfast into the ultimate in smells-incredible, just-like-Mom-would-make goodness.

products.title: Green Chile Bagel
products.description: Wake up your taste buds and send them south of the border with our Green Chile Gourmet Bagel. This southwest-inspired bagel features our super-melty blend of mozzarella, provolone and cheddar, roasted green chiles and the finishing zing of Asiago, parmesan and romano.

products.title: Honey Whole Wheat Bagel
products.description: A little whole grain, a little something sweet, a whole lot of nutritious flavor. Start your morning with a bagel made from healthy whole wheat flour, then sweetened to perfection with honey and brown sugar. Who said a bagel can’t be a healthy start to the day?

products.title: Plain Bagel
products.description: Simple? Yes. Boring? Never! A plain bagel is a timeless classic … it’s always in style, it goes with everything and it never disappoints. It’s the perfect canvas for whatever other yumminess you have in mind, so shmear it up any way you like.

products.title: Sesame Seed Bagel
products.description: Hungry? Just say “Open Sesame” and, POOF … bagel magic! Our Sesame Bagel is simple-yet-loveable, the favorite choice for hungry folks everywhere who want the perfect canvas to layer flavor onto. It’s a crunchy, satisfying magic carpet ride, if you will!

products.title: Six-Cheese Bagel
products.description: Embrace your inner “cheese” with our Six-Cheese Gourmet Bagel. We start with a melty mix of three cheese, mozzarella, provolone and cheddar, then finish it off with a tangier, tasty trio of asiago, parmesan and romano. One bite and you’ll smile and say cheese!

products.title: Half Dozen Bagel Box
products.description: Get the breakfast party started with a six-pack of tasty bagels! When you need big flavor for a smaller group, you can’t lose with our Half Dozen Bagel Box! Pick six of your favorite bagels and your #1 shmear. We promise the crowd will go wild!

products.title: Half Dozen Bagels Only
products.description: Half Dozen Bagels Only

products.title: Garden Veggie Reduced Fat Shmear
products.description: It’s like a salad in your shmear! We take our double-whipped, reduced fat shmear and layer in all of the crispy crunchy veggie goodness one bagel can handle! Little bits of carrots, bell peppers, celery, onions and scallions bring a pop of color and flavor.

products.title: Garlic Herb Reduced Fat Shmear
products.description: Why be boring when you can sass up your favorite bagel with this dynamic, never-dull classic shmear. We take our double-whipped, reduced fat shmear and add a bouquet of garden-fresh flavors, including garlic, spices, parsley, chervil, chives and dill.

products.title: Honey Almond Reduced Fat Shmear
products.description: Honey, what’s for breakfast? Your favorite Einstein Bros Bagel with the sweetest of morning shmears! Our double-whipped, reduced fat shmear gets a delish dose of naturally sweet honey and healthy almonds for a light and lovely bagel topping.

products.title: Jalapeno Salsa Reduced Fat Shmear
products.description: Is it hot in here or is it just my bagel?!? If you’re ready to spice things up a little, try our zesty Jalapeno Salsa Reduced Fat Shmear. Double-whipped, reduced fat shmear gets a healthy dose of Tex-Mex flavor with jalapeno peppers, diced tomatoes, red peppers, onions and garlic.

products.title: Onion and Chive Shmear
products.description: Zingy onion gets a bright dash of delish with herb-y chives in this classic one-two punch of a savory shmear. Top any bagel with a satisfying serving of garden-fresh flavor with our double-whipped Onion & Chive Shmear.

products.title: Plain Shmear
products.description: Our double-whipped Plain Shmear is like your favorite pair of jeans – it never goes out of style and it pairs perfectly with … everything! Mix and match our Plain Shmear with every kind of bagel and you’re sure to please every kind of taste bud.

products.title: Strawberry Reduced Fat Shmear
products.description: Searching for the “berry” best way to perk up your bagel? Light-as-air reduced fat, double-whipped shmear gets a delicious boost with a bounty of fresh strawberries blended in. It’s like a little taste of spring in every bite!

products.title: Smoked Salmon Shmear
products.description: Instantly take any bagel from basic to beyond fabulous with our Smoked Salmon Shmear. Savory, wonderfully mild cold-smoked salmon goes perfectly with the tang of our double-whipped shmear for a bagel topper that delights.

products.title: Applewood Bacon & Cheddar Egg Sandwich
products.description: If you’re going to go old school, do it up right with our Applewood Bacon and Cheddar Classic Breakfast Sandwich. A cage-free egg is topped with thick-sliced, applewood-smoked bacon that’s nitrite- and nitrate-free, then finished with melted-to-perfection cheddar cheese.

products.title: Turkey Sausage & Cheddar Egg Sandwich
products.description: Gobble gobble down our Turkey-Sausage & Cheddar Classic Breakfast Sandwich for a scrumptious meal that satisfies and boosts your day. Savory turkey sausage gets an elegant upgrade with our Caesar cheese blend of parmesan, romano and asiago, plus a bit extra cheddar for melted perfection!

products.title: Ham & Swiss Egg Sandwich
products.description: If you’re looking for the ideal savory combination to crown your bagel of choice, look no further than our Ham & Swiss Classic Breakfast Sandwich! This protein-packed meal has it all – a cage-free egg, stick-to-your-ribs sliced ham and melted Swiss cheese.

products.title: Cheddar Cheese Egg Sandwich
products.description: It doesn’t get any more classic than this! Pick your favorite bagel, toast it up right, then top it with only the best – a cage-free egg cooked to perfection and embellished with hits-your-taste buds-just right melted cheddar cheese.

products.title: Chorizo & Pepper Jack Egg Sandwich
products.description: If you sometimes need a kick in the morning, grab our Chorizo, Pepper Jack, Egg Sandwich. A spicy Chorizo patty topped with soft Pepper Jack cheese gives a traditional egg sandwich the right mix of flavors and spice.

products.title: Blueberry Muffin
products.description: Mouthwateringly good, our Blueberry Muffin goes beyond the ordinary snack. Fresh blueberries are nestled in a moist and tender muffin. What makes it extra special? You get a bit of satisfying “yum” in each bite with our streusel topping.

products.title: Cinnamon Chip Muffin
products.description: Can’t decide between a snack and a sweet? Grab our Cinnamon Chip Muffin for a little bit of both. Each fluffy muffin is infused with cinnamon chips for a simple flavor that perfectly satisfies. The finishing touch? Our unique cinnamon crunch streusel topping!

products.title: Sea Salt Chips
products.description: Sea Salt Chips

products.title: Heavenly Chocolate Chip Cookie
products.description: When mere chocolate chips aren’t enough, it’s our Chocolate Chunk Cookie to the rescue! Just like mom would make it, our classic cookie has those homemade flavors of vanilla and brown sugar that you crave, and it’s bursting with semisweet chocolate chunks!

products.title: Iced Sugar Cookie
products.description: There's nothing better than the buttery taste of our golden sugar cookies - except when they're topped with smooth sweet frosting. A perfect little treat individually packaged and ready to go.

products.title: Hash Brown Side
products.description: We’ve taken Hash Browns to another level. With 4 kinds of cheese and two of our classic shmears, all other Hash Browns have met their match. Add this awesome side to your next egg sandwich.

products.title: Yogurt Parfait
products.description: Yogurt Parfait

products.title: Turkey, Bacon & Avocado Sandwich
products.description: Don’t go “cold turkey” at lunch! Satisfy your hunger with our Turkey, Bacon & Avocado Signature Sandwich. Lean roasted turkey is dressed up with thick-cut bacon, creamy avocado, lettuce, tomato, and our unique roasted tomato spread, all on a fluffy, fresh-baked potato roll.

products.title: Turkey & Cheddar Sandwich
products.description: This deli-cious sandwich is the light and lovely answer to “What’s for lunch?” Roasted turkey goes from simple to satisfying with tangy cheddar cheese, crispy lettuce and freshly sliced tomato and red onion, plus mayo and deli mustard, all on a fresh-baked potato roll.

products.title: Ham & Swiss Sandwich
products.description: Smoked ham? Check! Swiss cheese? Check! This perfect deli sandwich has everything you need to scratch that classic ham and cheese itch! We complete this tasty twosome with crispy lettuce, red onion and tomato, mayo and deli mustard, and a fresh-baked, light-as-air potato roll.

products.title: Albacore Tuna Salad Sandwich
products.description: Sometimes only a true classic will satisfy your cravings! We start with mild albacore tuna, then blend it with the tried and true combo of crunchy celery and creamy mayo. It’s piled high with crispy tomato, lettuce and red onion. Timeless!

products.title: Tasty Turkey Sandwich
products.description: Looking for a light lunch that still leaves you feeling happy? We’ve gussied up roasted turkey with all the fixins – spinach, cucumber, lettuce, tomato and onion and chive shmear – and served it on an Asiago Bagel for a bit of cheesy goodness.

products.title: Nova Lox Sandwich
products.description: Nova Lox Sandwich

products.title: Pizza Bagel Pepperoni
products.description: Pizza, bagel … can’t decide? Put those hands together for our Pepperoni Pizza Bagel Sandwich. We’ve taken a Plain Bagel, topped it was our meltiest blend of mozzarella, provolone and cheddar, then added pepperoni, a smidge of pizza sauce and our Italian cheese trio of asiago, parmesan and romano.

products.title: Pizza Bagel Cheese
products.description: Craving a slice but want to go a bit more bagel-y? Our Cheese Pizza Bagel Sandwich scratches every itch! We’ve taken a Plain Bagel, topped it with SIX melty, gooey, tasty cheeses, then added a bit of pizza sauce for the savory finishing touch.

products.title: Farmhouse Egg Sandwich
products.description: Grab your pitchfork and dig in to this inspired-by-the farm breakfast combo. Our Farmhouse Signature Breakfast Sandwich starts with cage-free eggs, thick-cut bacon, smoked ham and cheddar cheese, then gets a back-to-the-farm finish with country pepper shmear on a Cheesy Hash Brown Gourmet Bagel

products.title: Chorizo Sunrise Egg Sandwich
products.description: Say “olé!” to the new day with our Chorizo Sunrise Signature Breakfast Sandwich! Take your taste buds on a trip south-of-the-border with savory chorizo sausage, luscious avocado, zingy pepper jack cheese, cage-free eggs and our jalapeno salsa shmear, all served on a Green Chile Gourmet Bagel.

products.title: All Nighter
products.description: All Nighter

products.title: Bacon, Avocado, & Tomato Sandwich
products.description: Looking for a mini splurge? Our chef-created bagel sandwich delivers incredible bacon-and-avo flavor, but with the lightness of fluffy egg whites. Your favorite bagel plus perfectly prepared egg whites get all dressed up with sliced tomato, fresh avocado, and sassy and savory roasted tomato spread.

products.title: Santa Fe Thintastic Egg White Sandwich
products.description: Spice up your breakfast with a healthy twist with our Santa Fe Egg White Breakfast Sandwich. Our Asiago Cheese Bagel is topped with turkey sausage, fresh egg whites, spicy pepper jack cheese, and our Jalapeño Salsa Reduced Fat Shmear. It's the kick you need in the morning.
